LUT cell CPU/DX/insn/loop1[2].a_dff/q_i_2__86, with 2 or more inputs, drives asynchronous preset/clear pin(s) CPU/muldiv/choose/q_reg/CLR. The LUT may glitch and trigger an unexpected reset, even if it is a properly timed path.
